episodes.title: The Black Axe Gang | Nigeria's Deadliest Cult | Hatchet Butchery & A Video As Gruesome As Ms Pacman
episodes.description:
The Black Axe is a notorious criminal organization that originated in Nigeria in the 1970s, particularly within university campuses. It began as a secretive fraternity, part of the broader Nigerian "confraternity" culture, initially aiming to fight oppression, colonial legacies, and promote solidarity among students. However, over the decades, the group evolved into a brutal, highly organized international crime syndicate involved in violent crime, extortion, human trafficking, drug smuggling, and fraud, both within Nigeria and globally.
